variable.name: PLATE_ID
variable.comment: Character field Blank = Field not filled in. Non-blank = Field filled in.

variable.name: FBN_I
variable.value: Set to missing because CV was above allowable limit

variable.name: CD5L_I
variable.value: Set to missing because CV was above allowable limit

variable.name: KLKB1_I
variable.value: Set to missing because CV was above allowable limit

variable.name: FBN
variable.comment: The lower detectable limit for FBN is 4.60E+06 pg/mL and the upper detectable limit is 1.96E+10 pg/mL. FBN values below or above these limits were set to the lower or upper detectable limit respectively. Use FBN_I to see what records are below and above these limits. FBN values were set to unknown if FBN_CV was greater than or equal to 18.5 for Offspring (IDTYPE = 1) or 18.4 for Gen 3 (IDTYPE = 3).

variable.name: FBN_CV
variable.comment: FBN_CV values were set to unknown if FBN_CV was greater than or equal to 18.5 for Offspring (IDTYPE = 1) or 18.4 for Gen 3 (IDTYPE = 3).

variable.name: CD5L
variable.comment: The lower detectable limit for CD5L is 2.24E+03 pg/mL and the upper detectable limit is 9.54E+06 pg/mL. CD5L values below or above these limits were set to the lower or upper detectable limit respectively. Use CD5L_I to see what records are below and above these limits. CD5L values were set to unknown if CD5L_CV was greater than or equal to 17.7 for Offspring (IDTYPE = 1) or 16.7 for Gen 3 (IDTYPE = 3).

variable.name: CD5L_CV
variable.comment: CD5L_CV values were set to unknown if CD5L_CV was greater than or equal to 17.7 for Offspring (IDTYPE = 1) or 16.7 for Gen 3 (IDTYPE = 3).

variable.name: KLKB1
variable.comment: The lower detectable limit for KLKB1 is 1.82E+05 pg/mL and the upper detectable limit is 2.13E+08 pg/mL. KLKB1 values below or above these limits were set to the lower or upper detectable limit respectively. Use KLKB1_I to see what records are below and above these limits. KLKB1 values were set to unknown if KLKB1_CV was greater than or equal to 23.0 for Offspring (IDTYPE = 1) or 26.0 for Gen 3 (IDTYPE = 3).

variable.name: KLKB1_CV
variable.comment: KLKB1_CV values were set to unknown if KLKB1_CV was greater than or equal to 23.0 for Offspring (IDTYPE = 1) or 26.0 for Gen 3 (IDTYPE = 3).

variable.name: RUN_DATE
variable.comment: Date includes month, day and year, however, coding manual displays only month and year to preserve confidentiality.
